editorial.title: New York
content: In the entertainment district, New York Marriott Marquis is in Manhattan, a walkable area in New York with great shopping. The area's natural beauty can be seen at Central Park and Bryant Park, while Broadway and Radio City Music Hall are cultural highlights. Check out an event or a game at Madison Square Garden, and consider making time for American Dream, a top attraction not to be missed. Guests appreciate the hotel's central location for the sightseeing. It's also convenient to public transportation: 49th St. Station is just steps away and Times Sq. - 42 St. Station is 5 minutes by foot.
